result.name: Exomic variants of a barley diverse panel SV274
result.description: Exomic variant dataset from a barley diverse panel,  SV274 accessions. More information for the panel is available from National Bioresource Project of Japan (NPRB; https://nbrp.jp/en/resource/barley-en/) and a published report (Sato et al., 2020; PMID: 32454448).
